START
create a class to hold the retail items data
parameters -> (items, units, price)

IMPORT retail item class into main file

main FUNCTION
        OUTPUT current date and time and the current directory
        ADD the data for the 3 items into 3 different variables

        OUTPUT the retail item information in the following format
        Description:  + items
        Units in Inventory: + units
        Price: + price

call main FUNCTION
